        <p>GAME 2</p>
        <p>Roger Clemens threw fastballs that reached 99 miles an hour, but drew even more attention for firing a broken bat in the direction of the Mets' Mike Piazza, pitching eight shutout innings and heightening the emotions of the Subway Series that is being controlled by the Yankees.</p>
